      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="decoration">garland</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs>. See <bibl><author>Isik</author> 176</bibl> for a full
description.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the <term lang="la">tabella</term> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.195</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.345</measure>) from which a
previous inscription has been erased. Line 1 on the upper moulding,
lines 2 ff. inscribed within the panel; lines 3-6, 9-12 impinge on the
right moulding. Very worn.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>Irregular and poorly formed, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.01-0.015</measure>; cursive <term>alpha</term>, <term>omega</term>
and <term>mu</term> used sporadically, square <term>sigma</term>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0333" exact="none" notBefore="0268">Late third/early fourth century</date> (titles).</p>
      </div>

